VISUAL:
AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; I know, but is it truly safe? &gt;&gt; I mean, that is pretty good. Squint your eyes a bit, and that\'s that\'s an HBO show. Now, I will say that Vio did the thing that it can do from time to time, which is jump from that first frame uh into essentially the same location. It'

[08:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'just gives us completely different shots. There is a way that we can utilize this to our advantage that we\'ll take a look at later on. Uh but yeah, we did not get that establishing opening shot. So, rerunning this as a JSON prompt, it does not come out perfect,'

[09:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'but it does actually lead to a pretty interesting trick. &gt;&gt; The bunker is our only chance. &gt;&gt; A chance to what? To be the last ones left.'

